casebody.data:
R. H. GORE v. NEWS-JOURNAL CORPORATION, a Florida corporation, et al. 9 So. (2nd) 809

June Term, 1942

October 2, 1942 En Banc McGune, Hiaasen <& Fleming, for appellant. Alfred A. Green, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

The appellant has failed clearly to show error in the decree of the chancellor, therefore, it is —

Affirmed.

BROWN, C. J., WHITFIELD, TERRELL, BUFORD, CHAPMAN, THOMAS and ADAMS, JJ., concur.,
